      *                  * Protocollo iniziale                         *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           perform   acc-prt-min-000      thru acc-prt-min-999        .
           if        w-cnt-acc-ric-sel    not  = spaces
                     go to acc-ric-sel-999.
