           perform   acc-prt-max-000      thru acc-prt-max-999        .
           if        w-cnt-acc-ric-sel    not  = spaces
                     go to acc-ric-sel-999.
           if        v-key                =    "UP  "
                     go to acc-ric-sel-100.
       acc-ric-sel-300.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Numero etichetta iniziale                   *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           perform   acc-eti-ini-000      thru acc-eti-ini-999        .
           if        w-cnt-acc-ric-sel    not  = spaces
                     go to acc-ric-sel-999.
           if        v-key                =    "UP  "
                     go to acc-ric-sel-200.
       acc-ric-sel-900.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Flag di controllo status impostazioni           *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
