      *    *-----------------------------------------------------------*
       prn-nes-ela-000.
           move      "WR"                 to   m-ope                  .
           move      "Nessuna etichetta da stampare !"
                                          to   m-msg                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mmessg"
                                         using m                      .
       prn-nes-ela-999.
           exit.

